---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout currentPath="/about">
	<section class="section">
		<div class="section-header">
			<span class="section-label">About Me</span>
			<h1 class="page-title">Games are at the intersection of design and technology.</h1>
			<p class="lead">I am a game developer with a strong background in interactive systems, full-stack development, and player experience design.  I wish to take the skills I have developed through my professional and academic work to create engaging and meaningful interactive experiences.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="highlight-grid">
			<div class="highlight-panel">
				<h2>My journey</h2>
				<p class="card-text">I started my college studies in architecture, and while I enjoyed the design process, there was something missing.  
					I found that missing piece by transitioning into computer science, where I discovered the power of combining design and technology to 
					create immersive interactive experiences.  Today, I have worked on game projects both through my master's program as well as with 
					incredible teams at companies like Mojang Studios and Booz Allen Hamilton.  As I further my career, I will continue to grow and refine 
					my skills in game development, and I hope to contribute to the creation of games that are not only fun to play, but also meaningful and 
					impactful.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="highlight-panel">
				<h2>What I Bring</h2>
				<ul class="feature-list">
					<li class="feature-item"><strong>Design systems</strong><span>Gameplay prototypes, progression loops, balance tuning, and a creative spirit to every project.</span></li>
					<li class="feature-item"><strong>Technical expertise</strong><span>C#, Unity, Unreal, and Godot workflows, version control, on top of a plethora of other programming languages and tools.</span></li>
					<li class="feature-item"><strong>Production focus</strong><span>Clear communication, milestone delivery, and creative problem-solving.  I will do whatever I can to be a team player.</span></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<div class="section-header">
			<span class="section-label">Skills & Mindset</span>
			<h2>Why I’m a strong candidate for your next project</h2>
		</div>

		<div class="grid-split">
			<div class="card">
				<h3 class="card-title">Creative Mindset</h3>
				<p class="card-text">I strive to create engaging interactive experiences unlike anything else.  My work is built to be fun, balanced, and versatile.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card">
				<h3 class="card-title">Production-Ready Delivery</h3>
				<p class="card-text">I prioritize clean implementation, documentation, and handoff so teams can move quickly without compromising quality.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card">
				<h3 class="card-title">Cross-Disciplinary Collaboration</h3>
				<p class="card-text">I communicate clearly with designers, artists, and engineers to keep scope realistic and deliver on shared creative goals.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card">
				<h3 class="card-title">Passion for Growth</h3>
				<p class="card-text">With every experience I have, I learn and improve.  I am always looking for ways to enhance my skills and contribute more effectively to my teams.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
